rsion: str\n    definition: dict = field(default_factory=dict)\n    enabled: bool = True\n```\n\n`app/models/workflow_run.py`：\n```python\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass WorkflowRun:\n    id: int\n    project_id: int\n    template_id: int\n    status: str = 'pending'\n```\n\n`app/models/workflow_step.py`：\n```python\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\n\n\n@dataclass\nclass WorkflowStep:\n    id: int\n    run_id: int\n    step_key: str\n    skill_name: str\n    status: str = 'pending'\n    retry_count: int = 0\n```\n\n**Step 4: 复测全部通过**\n```\npython -m pytest tests/ -v\n```\n\n**Step 5: 提交**\n```\ncd /c/Users/Administrator/legalflow-studio\ngit add apps/api/app/services apps/api/app/models/workflow_template.py apps/api/app/models/workflow_run.py apps/api/app/models/workflow_step.py apps/api/tests/test_workflow_state_machine.py\ngit commit -m \"feat: add workflow models and runtime state machine\"\n```\n\n输出：改动文件清单、测试结果、commit SHA。"},"uuid":"a8d8d524-bff7-4a53-a596-3cfe420e6531","timestamp":"2026-02-26T13:35:50.850Z"}
